//DANGER - if ANYONE gets your telegram bot with these settings he immediately has full control on your entire server!! 
EXAMPLE for settings for telegram to enable full exec
```
{
  tools: {
    profile: 'full',
    elevated: {
      enabled: true,
      allowFrom: {
        telegram: [
          '0123456789',
        ],
      },
    },
    exec: {
      security: 'full',
      ask: 'off',
    },
  }
}
```

might also need 
```
    telegram: {
      capabilities: {
        inlineButtons: 'dm',
      },
      execApprovals: {
        enabled: true,
        approvers: [
          0123456789,
        ],
        agentFilter: [
          'main',
        ],
        target: 'both',
      },
```

# Full Exec Pipeline

End-to-end flow chart of the OpenClaw exec pipeline, from tool invocation to execution decision.

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph INPUT["📥 Input: exec Tool Call"]
        CMD["Command<br/>host=auto|gateway|node|sandbox<br/>security=deny|allowlist|full<br/>ask=off|on-miss|always"]
    end

    subgraph PROFILE["🔧 Stage 1: tools.profile"]
        PROFILE_LOOKUP["Lookup base profile<br/>(from openclaw.json)"]
        PROFILE_MERGE["Merge profile allow/deny"]
    end

    subgraph POLICY["⚙️ Stage 2: Exec Policy"]
        GLOBAL["tools.exec<br/>(global)"]
        AGENT["agents.list[id].tools.exec<br/>(per-agent)"]
        MERGE_POLICY["Merge: requested<br/>security + ask"]
    end

    subgraph APPROVALS_FILE["📄 Stage 3: exec-approvals.json"]
        AF_DEFAULTS["defaults:<br/>security, ask, askFallback"]
        AF_AGENTS["agents:<br/>per-agent overrides"]
        AF_SOCKET["socket for<br/>approval daemon"]
    end

    subgraph ELEVATED["🚪 Stage 4: Elevated Gate"]
        ELEVATED_CHECK["tools.elevated<br/>enabled?"]
        SENDER_CHECK["sender in<br/>elevatedSenders?"]
    end

    subgraph ALLOWLIST["✅ Stage 5: Allowlist Matching"]
        SAFE_BIN["Safe bin?<br/>(ls, echo, etc)"]
        DENY_LIST["In deny list?"]
        ALLOW_LIST["In allow list?"]
        PATTERN["Pattern match?"]
    end

    subgraph APPROVAL["🤝 Stage 6: Approval Flow"]
        ASK_MODE["ask mode check"]
        APPROVAL_REQ["Create approval request"]
        APPROVAL_PEND["Pending...<br/>(timeout)"]
        APPROVAL_DECIDE["User approves/denies"]
    end

    subgraph DECISION["🎯 Stage 7: Decision"]
        DENY["❌ DENY<br/>Return error"]
        BYPASS["⚡ BYPASS<br/>Execute directly"]
        ASK["❓ ASK<br/>Wait for approval"]
    end

    subgraph EXEC["🔥 Stage 8: Execution"]
        EXEC_RUN["Run command<br/>via exec-wrapper"]
        EXEC_RESULT["Return output"]
    end

    %% Input to Profile
    INPUT --> PROFILE_LOOKUP
    PROFILE_LOOKUP --> PROFILE_MERGE

    %% Profile to Policy
    PROFILE_MERGE --> POLICY
    GLOBAL --> MERGE_POLICY
    AGENT --> MERGE_POLICY

    %% Policy to Approvals File
    MERGE_POLICY --> APPROVALS_FILE
    AF_DEFAULTS --> ELEVATED_CHECK
    AF_AGENTS --> ELEVATED_CHECK
    AF_SOCKET -.-> APPROVAL_REQ

    %% Elevated Gate
    ELEVATED_CHECK -->|yes| SENDER_CHECK
    ELEVATED_CHECK -->|no| ALLOW_LIST
    SENDER_CHECK -->|yes| ALLOW_LIST
    SENDER_CHECK -->|no| ASK_MODE

    %% Allowlist
    SAFE_BIN -->|yes| BYPASS
    SAFE_BIN -->|no| DENY_LIST
    DENY_LIST -->|yes| DENY
    DENY_LIST -->|no| ALLOW_LIST
    ALLOW_LIST -->|yes| PATTERN
    ALLOW_LIST -->|no| ASK_MODE

    PATTERN -->|match| BYPASS
    PATTERN -->|no match| ASK_MODE

    %% Approval Flow
    ASK_MODE -->|ask=off| DENY
    ASK_MODE -->|ask=on-miss| ALLOW_LIST
    ASK_MODE -->|ask=always| APPROVAL_REQ

    APPROVAL_REQ --> APPROVAL_PEND
    APPROVAL_PEND -->|timeout| DENY
    APPROVAL_PEND --> APPROVAL_DECIDE

    APPROVAL_DECIDE -->|approve| BYPASS
    APPROVAL_DECIDE -->|deny| DENY

    %% Execution
    BYPASS --> EXEC_RUN
    EXEC_RUN --> EXEC_RESULT
```

