## Quick Access

### Full Exec Access (Bypass All Approvals)

```bash
# 1. Set full profile
openclaw config set tools.profile full

# 2. Set exec host to gateway
openclaw config set tools.exec.host gateway

# 3. Set security to full
openclaw config set tools.exec.security full

# 4. Disable approval prompts
openclaw config set tools.exec.ask off

# 5. Restart gateway
openclaw gateway restart

# 6. Enter TUI
openclaw tui --session main
```

### Other Quick Commands

```bash
# Check current exec policy
openclaw approvals status

# View allowlist
openclaw approvals list

# Add an allowlist entry
openclaw approvals allow "myagent" --pattern "ls *"

# Test a command (dry run)
openclaw exec --dry-run "ls -la"
```
